The paper focuses on open-domain question answering using a relational graph neural network with attention mechanism and hierarchical representation learning. This involves natural language processing (NLP), machine learning (ML), and information retrieval (IR) techniques, which are commonly associated with the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Databases (cs.DB).
